    "Article https://doi.org/10.1038/s41592-024-02426-z",
    "for individual neurons at several time offsets from the snapshot using the delta query logic.",
    "The resulting measurements can be categorized into three groups.",
    "First, we obtained measurements for presynapse queries of FlyWire neurons that were aligned with a snapshot (median = 525 ms, N = 121,400; Fig. 5d).",
    "Second, we gathered timings for nonsnapshot aligned queries where the query neuron did not see any edits since the snapshot version, although its synaptic partners may have (median = 978 ms, N = 127,775)."
